Kathleen Clifford https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kathleen_Clifford 0 Kathleen Clifford (February 16, 1887 – December 28, 1962) was an American vaudeville and Broadway stage and film actress of the early twentieth century. She was known for her skills as a male impersonator.
